{"tid":2452392,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"呢排點解咁多買家撻訂","createTime":"2021-03-18T21:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T04:58:53.000Z","uid":24730,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2b8d60ac0735769e437654187351953efbd18841","tid":2452392,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T21:56:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">匯璽 III 開放式戶買家撻大訂　料損失逾69萬</span><br />\n<br />\n新地（0016）旗下南昌站匯璽 III ，新錄得一宗撻訂個案，料買家遭殺訂近70萬元。據成交紀錄冊顯示，單位為6座45樓F室，面積271平方呎，連21平方呎露台，屬開放式間隔，在2019年以698.08萬元成交，呎價約25,759元，買家當時選用建築期付款計劃。不過，於近日撻大訂，料損失10%訂金，即69.808萬元。<br />\n此外，同系的日出康城晉海 II 近日亦錄撻訂，單位為3B座30樓D室，面積477平方呎，屬兩房間隔，在2018年以805.56萬元成交，呎價約16,888元，買家採用180天即供付款計劃。不過，買家亦近日選擇撻訂，料損失10%訂金，即涉80.556萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/600861/%E5%8C%AF%E7%92%BD-iii-%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E5%BC%8F%E6%88%B6%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6%E6%92%BB%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%82-%E6%96%99%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1%E9%80%BE69%E8%90%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E7%2594%25A2%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%2F600861%2F%25E5%258C%25AF%25E7%2592%25BD-iii-%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25BC%258F%25E6%2588%25B6%25E8%25B2%25B7%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2592%25BB%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A8%2582-%25E6%2596%2599%25E6%2590%258D%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E9%2580%25BE69%25E8%2590%25AC&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSvRe10cHvJvhFGsNMWslaGA%3D&h=df36d087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82/600861/%E5%8C%AF%E7%92%BD-iii-%E9%96%8B%E6%94%BE%E5%BC%8F%E6%88%B6%E8%B2%B7%E5%AE%B6%E6%92%BB%E5%A4%A7%E8%A8%82-%E6%96%99%E6%90%8D%E5%A4%B1%E9%80%BE69%E8%90%AC</a><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><br />\n白石角海日灣三房買家入市不足兩周撻訂　料損失逾152萬</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n億京集團旗下白石角海日灣已屆現樓，新近錄得一宗撻訂，料買家遭殺訂逾152萬元。單位為COURT A第2座8樓A室，面積1,329平方呎，屬三房間隔。據一手成交紀錄冊顥示，單位在本月初（5日）以3,052.3萬元成交，呎價約22,967元，並採用105天付款計劃。不過，買家近日選擇撻訂，料損失5%訂金，即約152.615萬元。"},{"pid":"776f86ff2095924ad748ab952f841e02318f9e79","tid":2452392,"uid":4242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T22:34:03.000Z","msg":"海日灣係唔係歷史上殺訂得最多金額既樓盤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8a48a385f71f2b9fea60146b0ebb6827a2994e1","tid":2452392,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T22:39:08.000Z","msg":"琴日公布嘅CCI掉頭跌了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8192xtH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8192xtH.png&h=216ca24b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0R4aGm4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0R4aGm4.png&h=bc9b1966&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bab9d7e404912e9d6b6eeeb0634438610c58cd43","tid":2452392,"uid":291750,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T22:57:27.000Z","msg":"上唔到會？過唔到壓測？"},{"pid":"555ba3b09cb173699baf292798a77d0820858857","tid":2452392,"uid":24730,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f8a48a385f71f2b9fea60146b0ebb6827a2994e1","tid":2452392,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T22:39:08.000Z","msg":"琴日公布嘅CCI掉頭跌了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8192xtH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8192xtH.png&h=216ca24b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0R4aGm4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0R4aGm4.png&h=bc9b1966&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T23:06:13.000Z","msg":"對比CCI及CCL嘅差額，就知道CCL點樣呃人<br />\n<br />\nCCI係根據正式買賣合約註冊數據計算，CCL則純屬中原喺未有正式數據前「領先估計」嘅數字。<br />\n<br />\n請睇番以下CCL喺今年一月份「領先估計」當月嘅指數，平均約為175.98<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AGoKLVC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAGoKLVC.png&h=b9184abc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但琴日公布嘅CCI，一月份指數實際上只有173.67，兩者相差達2.31個百分點。樓市實際上係跌，但CCL就呃你係升。報紙地產版永遠只會報導「靠估」嘅CCL，但唔會報導較準確嘅CCI，亦唔會講畀你知CCL其實成日「估」大咗條數，所以你以為樓市升緊，實際上係跌緊"},{"pid":"9eaa87d8a613b42abf0dad25998f456159ac3e21","tid":2452392,"uid":124479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:23:00.000Z","msg":"Molamola 樓災啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75fad830cbe97f5c608667e44fadfb4528f8e8d4","tid":2452392,"uid":249170,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:48:59.000Z","msg":"應該筆錢唔係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由第二個地方轉落黎香港果陣遇到重重困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd5440c3a30741c40c82848ce1b5b642d3126c42","tid":2452392,"uid":245027,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLj9XDv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLj9XDv.png&h=34c44c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最多話係打平走<br />\n同埋樓市係一月起開始升<br />\n你俾一月數據黎有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實你咁熱愛移民<br />\n咁關心香港樓市做咩"},{"pid":"517e8b60031f99253a2e1581757ee12969d6dadd","tid":2452392,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fd5440c3a30741c40c82848ce1b5b642d3126c42","tid":2452392,"uid":245027,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T00:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gLj9XDv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgLj9XDv.png&h=34c44c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最多話係打平走<br />\n同埋樓市係一月起開始升<br />\n你俾一月數據黎有咩用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實你咁熱愛移民<br />\n咁關心香港樓市做咩"},"citedB